one joker after another.

117
00:06:37,041 --> 00:06:39,625
I think the longest any one
guy lasted was about a week.

118
00:06:39,708 --> 00:06:42,041
And the guy that had the
shortest relationship with her?

119
00:06:42,125 --> 00:06:43,500
He asked her out,
she said okay,

120
00:06:43,583 --> 00:06:46,000
and it ended five minutes later.

121
00:06:46,083 --> 00:06:48,916
I don't have any time to deal
with ordinary humans!

122
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:51,583
[TANIGUCHI] Then why the hell'd
you say okay?

123
00:06:51,666 --> 00:06:52,625
Hmm?

124
00:06:52,708 --> 00:06:54,541
I mean, that's what
I heard, really!

125
00:06:54,625 --> 00:06:56,875
I don't know why, but she
never turns a guy down

126
00:06:56,958 --> 00:06:58,416
when he steps up to ask her out.

127
00:06:58,500 --> 00:07:01,041
And so, before you get any
bright ideas, buddy,

128
00:07:01,125 --> 00:07:03,041
take my advice:

129
00:07:03,125 --> 00:07:04,291
forget it.

130
00:07:04,375 --> 00:07:06,000
[KYON]
Forget it? What's to forget

131
00:07:06,083 --> 00:07:08,291
when I haven't even
though about it?

132
00:07:10,333 --> 00:07:12,125
[TANIGUCHI] If you were me,
there's only one girl

133
00:07:12,208 --> 00:07:14,708
in this class to go after.
And that's her.

134
00:07:16,125 --> 00:07:18,291
[TANIGUCHI] Ryoko Asakura.
And I'm telling ya,

135
00:07:18,375 --> 00:07:21,416
