138
00:07:24,791 --> 00:07:27,041
Heck yeah! I ranked
'em all from A to D

139
00:07:27,125 --> 00:07:29,500
and I even went so far as
to memorize the full names

140
00:07:29,583 --> 00:07:31,166
of all the A-list girls, buddy.

141
00:07:31,250 --> 00:07:33,083
Really? So what ranking
did Asakura get?

142
00:07:33,166 --> 00:07:34,750
She gets Double-A plus!

143
00:07:34,833 --> 00:07:38,375
On top of being gorgeous, I bet
her personality is wonderful.

144
00:07:40,458 --> 00:07:41,791
[panting]

145
00:07:41,875 --> 00:07:44,083
[BOYS murmuring]

146
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:45,875
[KYON]
Now, all this was happening

147
00:07:45,958 --> 00:07:48,791
when Haruhi Suzumiya was
still acting sorta normal.

148
00:07:48,875 --> 00:07:51,458
For that whole month, even
I was feeling pretty good.

149
00:07:51,541 --> 00:07:53,583
However, it should be noted
that bits and pieces

150
00:07:53,666 --> 00:07:55,958
