152
00:07:58,291 --> 00:08:02,666
Haruhi Eccentricity number 1:
A different hairstyle everyday.

153
00:08:02,750 --> 00:08:03,375
Monday.

154
00:08:03,458 --> 00:08:04,125
Tuesday.

155
00:08:04,208 --> 00:08:04,916
Wednesday.

156
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:05,666
Thursday.

157
00:08:05,750 --> 00:08:06,833
Friday.

158
00:08:06,916 --> 00:08:08,166
As the days passed,
the number of places

159
00:08:08,250 --> 00:08:09,750
she'd tie off her
hair increased.

160
00:08:09,833 --> 00:08:11,416
On Monday, she resets her hair,

161
00:08:11,500 --> 00:08:13,916
and then adds off a tie-off
point each day until Friday.

162
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,875
