164
00:08:19,416 --> 00:08:21,125
[KYON]
Haruhi Eccentricity number 2:

165
00:08:21,208 --> 00:08:24,250
Our PE classe is seperated
into boys and girls.

166
00:08:24,333 --> 00:08:25,500
When changing into uniforms,

167
00:08:25,583 --> 00:08:27,250
