numbered classrooms

168
00:08:27,333 --> 00:08:28,833
and boys used the even numbers.

169
00:08:28,916 --> 00:08:31,166
It didn't matter that guys
were standing around,

170
00:08:31,250 --> 00:08:34,000
she'd just start changing
out of her school uniform.

171
00:08:34,083 --> 00:08:36,375
[STUDENTS screaming]

172
00:08:40,083 --> 00:08:42,041
[KYON]
To Haruhi, guys were pretty much

173
00:08:42,125 --> 00:08:44,208
the same as a bag of potatoes.

174
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:49,958
[KYON] Eccentricity number 3:
It was rather irritating

175
00:08:50,041 --> 00:08:51,541
that Haruhi joined
every team in

176
00:08:51,625 --> 00:08:55,000
