the sports clubs lobbied

178
00:08:57,166 --> 00:08:59,041
for her to join their
respective teams,

179
00:08:59,125 --> 00:09:01,291
and she'd turned
every one of 'em down.

180
00:09:01,375 --> 00:09:04,541
She'd change clubs on a daily
basis depending on her mood.

181
00:09:04,625 --> 00:09:06,375
In the end though,
she didn't remain a member

182
00:09:06,458 --> 00:09:08,333
of a single one of the clubs.

183
00:09:08,416 --> 00:09:11,458
I mean, what the hell does
she wanna do anyway?

184
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:15,000
[KYON] And before I knew it,
it was the day after

185
