186
00:09:16,041 --> 00:09:17,500
[TANIGUCHI]
Kyon! What's up?

187
00:09:17,583 --> 00:09:18,833
Hey.

188
00:09:18,916 --> 00:09:21,333
[KYON] And by the way, Kyon?
That's my nickname.

189
00:09:21,416 --> 00:09:24,458
And I really wish people would
stop calling me that already.

190
00:09:28,208 --> 00:09:30,708
[KYON] Oh. I guess today's
Wednesday, isn't it?

191
00:09:30,791 --> 00:09:34,250
And with that thought, something
must've snapped inside me.

192
00:09:34,333 --> 00:09:36,833
I can't think of
any reason why...

193
00:09:36,916 --> 00:09:38,750
So, do you cahnge
your hairstyle everyday

194
00:09:38,833 --> 00:09:40,500
